            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1614615190676-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>crispy soy basa</strong> with the<strong> cooked</strong> <strong>rice </strong>and <strong>black bean greens </strong>to the side and pour any <strong>remaining black bean sauce </strong>over the greens</p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into a small bowl and turn out</p><p>Sprinkle the <strong>crispy ginger & garlic</strong> and <strong>sliced spring onion</strong> over the crispy soy basa and rice</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
